            <h2>How can I participate</h2>
            <p>It’s up to you!</p>
            <p>Simply fill in the form below to enter. How you achieve your distance is up to you!</p>
            <p>All participants will be part of a team.&nbsp;The minimum number needed to create a team is 2 participants, there is no maximum number. If your team goes over the 26.2 miles that is OK!</p>
            <p>Your distance can be achieved by any type of movement that you are capable of: walk, run, roll over the course of the 4-day event. Participants may be assisted or unassisted. If an individual is assisted, both participants may count their distances and register as separate teammates. A participant may also join multiple teams and contribute separate distances to each team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
